  "title": "Festive Helper (Temp)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Join Us as a Retail Festive Helper!</strong><br />Love the festive season and working in a lively retail environment? We’re looking for energetic and reliable individuals to join our team and help us prepare for <strong>Chinese New Year sales</strong>!</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />✅ Assist in the preparation and setup for Chinese New Year sales.<br />✅ Support in product development and packaging of festive items.<br />✅ Help with loading and unloading of plants and other items.<br />✅ Maintain cleanliness and organization of the sales floor.<br />✅ Provide friendly and helpful customer service.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br />✅ Positive attitude and team player.<br />✅ Physically fit and comfortable with hands-on work.<br />✅ Able to work on weekends and public holidays.<br />✅ Willing to work during festive seasons (including Chinese New Year’s Eve).<br />✅ No experience needed – training will be provided!</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Bedok<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 9am – 7pm<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $12/hr</p>",
